It has a 16 horsepower Koler gas motor with electric starter which sits at midship and a little bronze helm to steer the boat.  Great little runabout and a real head turner.  We just got done with the coeur d'alene wooden boat festival where we had people stopping all day to gawk and ask questions.  Great for cruising the lake and going out for a picnic. We have had four 200 lb adults plus gear onboard with no worries.  Full keel all the way to the shaft packing and then a bronze prop and rudder.
